{"tid":1113012,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"清邁玩高空飛索 安全扣突斷裂 25歲肥男墮斃","createTime":"2019-04-17T17:17:20.000Z","updateTime":"2019-04-18T00:18:14.000Z","uid":236891,"like":13,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"3d814f80fd2604b1af62f4625f8ede7c00224ca2","tid":1113012,"uid":236891,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-17T17:17:20.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.am730.com.hk/news/新聞/【玩出人命】高空飛索安全扣斷裂-加男50米高空墮下亡-169601\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.am730.com.hk%2Fnews%2F%E6%96%B0%E8%81%9E%2F%E3%80%90%E7%8E%A9%E5%87%BA%E4%BA%BA%E5%91%BD%E3%80%91%E9%AB%98%E7%A9%BA%E9%A3%9B%E7%B4%A2%E5%AE%89%E5%85%A8%E6%89%A3%E6%96%B7%E8%A3%82-%E5%8A%A0%E7%94%B750%E7%B1%B3%E9%AB%98%E7%A9%BA%E5%A2%AE%E4%B8%8B%E4%BA%A1-169601&d=hObUr7UKzm7jHRUyz9oMSAg0DHywPMniAnH04N%2BeXdM%3D&h=12cb520c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.am730.com.hk/news/新聞/【玩出人命】高空飛索安全扣斷裂-加男50米高空墮下亡-169601</a><br />\n<br />\n玩高空飛索隨時玩出人命，加拿大25歲死肥鳩男子查爾斯(Spencer Charles)，上周六在泰國清邁旅遊期間，參與叢林高空飛索活動，索纜卻在滑行途中折斷，令他從50米高空墮下，跌到下方一條小溪身亡。高空飛索規定體重逾275磅的人士不能參與，當地警方最初公布死者重約397磅，懷疑索纜的安全鎖扣斷裂是因為無法承受死者的體重，但其後則確認為264磅，未有超出限制，現正繼續調查意外成因。叢林高空飛索營運商Flight of the Gibbon承諾向家屬作賠償，而叢林高空飛索活動則暫停直至當局批准重開。"},{"pid":"e3c4fef1af7ea6ea7cfd42f265f9f40111b31df2","tid":1113012,"uid":191815,"like":10,"dislike":1,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-17T17:18:48.000Z","msg":"咁撚肥都唔怕死<br />\n值嘅"},{"pid":"15bd256d76082b43e45d5eaacc9794897858d922","tid":1113012,"uid":54181,"like":14,"dislike":0,"score":14,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-17T17:21:59.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"b6c8408e5545abad826b0e350c4b157805216579","tid":1113012,"uid":46155,"like":6,"dislike":1,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-17T17:25:01.000Z","msg":"死肥仔"},{"pid":"35e0f48ea217e9be4450f74fd50e3c4060a1d1bf","tid":1113012,"uid":8766,"like":10,"dislike":1,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-17T17:26:14.000Z","msg":"加拿大25歲死肥鳩男子<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4a8